```

#### 5ï¸âƒ£ **Auto-Save Notes**
Persist user input automatically to **prevent accidental loss**.

**Key Hint:**  
Use `useEffect()` to sync notes with local storage:
```jsx
useEffect(() => {
  localStorage.setItem("Notes", JSON.stringify(notes));
}, [notes]);
```

